Class Staff

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscm12.cafe94.Staff

  • public class Staff
extends java.lang.Object
    [ManageStaff] Manage staff class is responsible for being the blank slate for staff information. It receives and fills itself with SQL database for staff objects. The data is used by @getManageStaffTable and @getStaffTable in the Controller class.
